{
  "stem": "27409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was-- this is called conscripting, assembling, uh, soldiers for return-- dissent, stragglers in the forest for return, dissent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I was-- was glad to have a commander.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went after him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He put us-- his tank.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we broke through to Brody, that was quite a town in former Poland, Galicia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, we didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were three tanks which broke through the lines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went on, straight on-- it's about 30 miles-- to, uh, towards Lviv.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is the capital of Galicia, a large town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we enter the town, the Germans were in the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stopped in front-- I remember well-- and stopped in front of the prison, local prison.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were, uh, Ukrainian guards there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "German, I didn't see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We stormed the prison.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an, uh, idea of mine to storm the prison because we were only three tanks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were only three tanks, were about 50 soldiers infan-- infantry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We opened the gates, they finished off the guards and took their arms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we kept the town till about-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "More tanks arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we started cleaning the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they found we are so good, so they decided to go ahead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was quick-moving front.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went towards the Sian, the river Sian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the mean time, I got the rank of sergeant, my first advancement in the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, uh, we went into Sian, [INAUDIBLE] was bitter fighting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We crossed the Sian, the river Sian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't expect us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a hill up in the town, toward the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was only a few hours in the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were sitting and waiting for replenishment, other soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
